                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Cordless leg massager with <strong>3 compression levels</strong>, built-in heat, and auto shut-off. </p><p>Designed to <strong>relieve soreness, swelling</strong>, and tension in the calves anytime, anywhere.</p><ul><li>Bullet</li><li>23</li><li>45</li><li>45</li></ul>",
